import React from 'react'
import { Header, Modal } from 'semantic-ui-react'

const WarningModal = () => (
  <Modal trigger={props.isModalOpen}>
    <Modal.Content>
      <Modal.Description>
        <Header>Please Select An Event</Header>
      </Modal.Description>
    </Modal.Content>
  </Modal>
)

export default WarningModal;
